Cell["\<\
This document is a practical  introduction to designing macro-scale neural \
models built around the topological associative memory described at \
creatingintelligence.org.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"87579e7b-f6a0-41f8-82c2-9eb95fc7b7df"],

Cell["\<\
From a computational point of view, circuits represent stateful machines for \
processing hyperdimensional sparse distributed representations. \
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"5b172065-2507-41b6-9140-ff1ce668f5e3"],

Cell["\<\
A compact dataflow description language  fully specifies circuits composed of \
standardized building blocks:\
