Cell["Circuit Connections", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"959a6ecf-47ef-4108-975e-418b56994403"],

Cell["\<\
The data paths connecting circuit components can be flexibly configured to \
transport, transform,
route and merge data. Dataflow options are attached to the slot numbers in \
the components\[CloseCurlyQuote] \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]receive\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] argument. \
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"bca56f70-d3f4-4a79-87ac-b280444af2dc"],

Cell["\<\
In this example, we tag the pathway with \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]R\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote], which indicates stochastic rate limiting:\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"eefb1d8a-dc61-4605-9820-6a102184e3dd"],

