Cell["\<\
Pathways convey either sets (the default) or multisets. Multiset pathways may \
carry duplicate elements, as well as negative entries indicating inhibitory \
signals. \
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"24f86e65-a3d0-4921-928f-345cc98b18a4"],

Cell["\<\
Multiset paths are tagged with \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]+\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote] and displayed as thick \
colored lines:\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"ae13ba10-7aea-4739-9948-d93e1080d20b"],

