Cell["\<\
An external function, plugged into the input node\[CloseCurlyQuote]s \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]receive\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] slot, is applied to \
the raw input before encoding. This mechanism may serve as a preprocessing \
step, or as a source of external data. Similarly, a postprocessing function \
can be plugged in the output node\[CloseCurlyQuote]s \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]send\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] slot.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"293c75a3-362d-4dd8-829c-f74280ddad3b"],

Cell["\<\
Here we source a date string from an externally defined function, encode it \
as an SHR, and decode the output back to the string. \
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"51a2a230-a708-4780-b7e2-5d45107f0c5c"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

