Cell["\<\
Apply a permutation to the second output. The order in which input and output \
nodes appear in the dataflow description matches the order of the respective \
input and output sequences.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"7826b226-ec8b-4e2c-bfdd-fcd5f6c285eb"],

