Cell["Nested Circuits", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"a28cb523-7a01-4df1-b180-37a2ec2578c6"],

Cell["\<\
This framework allows circuits to be logically nested, enabling modular \
designs based on reusable subnetworks.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"5ffbb9d1-4b30-43b5-8d73-d6e31031158a"],

Cell["\<\
