Cell["\<\
Paths tagged with strings of the from \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]@10...\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] act as temporal gates with respect to the circuit\
\[CloseCurlyQuote]s cycle counter. \
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"42dc765e-7fdb-4a9a-85ea-c1e1a67816bc"],

Cell["\<\
This circuit lets its input pass through in two out of three cycles:\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"2e8d2f9c-1dad-4f24-a6a0-1c641d68f778"],

