Cell["\<\
Inhibitory signals are delayed much like excitatory elements. Here, the \
outgoing path is marked as a multiset edge. Therefore, it preserves the \
negatives:\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"fc333b4c-0081-4510-8059-f2903f18e834"],

