Cell["\<\
Here is a reverberatory circuit that bounces signals between two delay nodes, \
toggling  two states in the absence of new input. As the incoming pathway \
takes priority over the feedback, no rate decimation is needed.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"e9414c0a-96f0-4db1-918d-fa10d5921e18"],

