Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Stand-alone kwta component", "Subsubsection",ExpressionUUID->"7672c362-fc29-4382-8e81-2d43c5c86370"],

Cell["\<\
The k-winners-take-all (\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]kwta\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]) \
component computes a majority vote across multiple inputs and multiple \
cycles, returning the top-k ranked elements. The parameter \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]k\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] is taken to be the component\
\[CloseCurlyQuote]s output population. By default, only on the current cycle \
is taken into account:\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"f49e6fb9-b3da-4d7c-91fc-0c95f87e39d5"],

