Cell["\<\
Here is an item memory for sparse distributed representations (SDRs), using \
an explicit setting T=10 for the pattern matching threshold. If no update \
rule is specified in the auto-associative memory component, the default \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]replacement\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] is assumed. \
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"e3b5c163-c93d-4a97-93e1-543c8310898f"],

