Cell["Complement update", "Subsubsection",ExpressionUUID->"a39f92f6-a19e-498d-9762-33f2cca94213"],

Cell["\<\
The \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]complement\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] update rule \
removes the input from the retrieved pattern.\
