Cell["Hyper-Associative Memory", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"39526513-a8cf-43f3-b724-9813ca67c2d9"],

Cell["\<\
This sets up an auto-associative memory using the \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]complement\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] update rule. The \
system learns new information if it lies in the specified population range \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]L\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote].\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"c4f6195d-8e16-4351-aa10-578286913b34"],

