Cell["This circuit in JSON format:", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"20cc23dc-6670-4f42-a40c-87e6b410c796"],

Cell["\<\

{
  \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]$schema\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]https://creatingintelligence.org/schemas/circuit-v1.\
json\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote],

  \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]hyperparameters\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: {\
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]default\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: [2000, 8]},

  \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]dataflow\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: [
    {\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]component\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]input\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote], \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]arguments\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: [\
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]codec\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]], \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]send\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: [11]},

    {\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]component\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]delay\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote], \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]send\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: [21], \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]receive\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: [11]},

    {\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]component\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]heteroencoder\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote], \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]send\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: [51], \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]receive\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: [11, 21]},

    {\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]component\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]delay\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote], \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]send\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: [61], \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]receive\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: [[51, {\
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]slot\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: 62, \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]tags\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: \
[\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]permute\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]]}]]},

    {\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]component\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]delay\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote], \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]options\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: {\
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]R\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: 30}, \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]send\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: [62], \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]receive\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: [61]},

    {\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]component\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]predictor\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote], \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]send\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: [101], \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]receive\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: [11, [11, 61]]},

    {\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]component\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]output\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote], \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]arguments\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: [\
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]codec\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]], \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]receive\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]: [101]}
  ]
}\
\>", "Text",
